    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,724 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio [515 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega/ryu-ga-gotoku-studio">Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio</a> will host <em><a title="Games > Yakuza Kiwami 3 &amp; Dark Ties [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/yakuza-kiwami-3-dark-ties">Yakuza Kiwami 3 &amp; Dark Ties</a></em> Direct on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20251223T0100" target="_blank">December 22 at 5:00 p.m. PT / 8:00 p.m. ET</a>, the companies <a href="https://twitter.com/RGGStudio/status/2001351859848495484" target="_blank">announced</a>. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SEGA_West" target="_blank">YouTube</a> and <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/sega" target="_blank">Twitch</a>. <span id="more-1015914"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature a deep dive on the upcoming two-in-one title, including new features, experiences, and gameplay from both games.</p><p><em>Yakuza Kiwami 3 &amp; Dark Ties</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,095 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,599 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,489 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [810 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,131 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3937550/Yakuza_Kiwami_3__Dark_Ties/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on February 12, 2026.</p></div>

        
    
